moj otac je bio bolestan.

106
00:11:47,692 --> 00:11:51,112
Umro je dok sam bila veoma mlada.

107
00:11:51,112 --> 00:11:52,947
Pardon.

108
00:11:52,947 --> 00:11:57,451
