116
00:12:43,787 --> 00:12:46,205
Ja sam.
G-dica Braun.

117
00:12:46,205 --> 00:12:51,085
Imam nesto za gospodina Kitsa.

118
00:12:51,085 --> 00:12:53,713
Ostavite ispred vrata.

119
00:12:53,713 --> 00:12:57,091
Da li je on tu?
- Radimo, g-dice Bron.

120
00:12:57,091 --> 00:13:01,304
Imam nešto za vašeg brata, g. Kits.

121
00:13:01,304 --> 00:13:06,600
Neka ude.
Braun!

122
00:13:14,232 --> 00:13:17,027
Vi ste odvratni majmun.

123
00:13:17,027 --> 00:13:22,949
Pazite se,
ulazite u kavez sa majmunom.

124
00:13:22,949 --> 00:13:26,243
Sedite pored mene g-dice Bron.

125
00:13:26,243 --> 00:13:31,790
Osecam da je moja
perspektiva u svetu veoma slaba.

126
00:13:31,790 --> 00:13:36,503
Ova soba se retko cisti.

127
00:13:37,421 --> 00:13:40,006
Molim Vas, probajte jedan.

128
00:13:40,006 --> 00:13:46,429
Razmišljam, kada bi se on udavio njima...

129
00:13:46,429 --> 00:13:50,183
Ne! Uzmi još jedan
i kunem se ugrišcu te.

130
00:13:50,183 --> 00:13:53,436
Pazi se.
Ima oštre zube.

131
00:13:53,436 --> 00:13:57,982
Zarila je zube u moju jadnu
pesmu i rastrgla je na komade.

132
00:13:58,023 --> 00:14:02,528
Žao mi je što nisam sasvim uspela da
zavolim vaš "Endimion", g. Kits.

133
00:14:02,570 --> 00:14:04,571
Možda Vam nisam rekla..

134
00:14:04,571 --> 00:14:10,744
ali mislim da je pocetak
Vaše pesme savršen.

135
00:14:10,744 --> 00:14:14,914
Ne napuštajte nas. Kao što vidite
i sami, ništa ne radimo.

136
00:14:14,914 --> 00:14:18,418
Po ceo dan ležimo i
cekamo inspiraciju.

137
00:14:18,418 --> 00:14:22,630
Molim Vas, recite mi šta
bi trebalo da radim.

138
00:14:22,630 --> 00:14:26,342
g-dice Bron,

139
00:14:26,342 --> 00:14:31,222
mi majmuni samo želimo malo društva.

140
00:14:34,808 --> 00:14:39,813
Dala sam mu biskvite.

141
00:14:39,813 --> 00:14:42,274
G. Braun je...

142
00:14:42,274 --> 00:14:44,734
Ako smo završili sa ljutnjom,

143
00:14:44,734 --> 00:14:46,486
dodite da pozdravite Toma.

144
00:14:46,486 --> 00:14:48,238
Popravice mu raspoloženje.

145
00:14:48,238 --> 00:14:49,864
Moramo da pitamo mamu.

146
00:14:49,864 --> 00:14:52,534
Ne moramo, Tuts.
- Moramo.

147
00:14:52,534 --> 00:14:54,160
Je li tako, Semjuel?

148
00:14:54,160 --> 00:14:56,704
Moramo se držati zajedno.

149
00:14:56,704 --> 00:14:58,998
Ja idem.

150
00:14:58,998 --> 00:15:03,169
Morate da podete sa mnom.

151
00:15:04,045 --> 00:15:07,839
Želite li da idemo stazom,
ili kroz šumu?

152
00:15:07,839 --> 00:15:14,095
Istražio sam sve ove puteve,
kojih ima više nego vaših trepavica.

153
00:15:14,137 --> 00:15:19,184
Moje trepavice?

154
00:15:20,643 --> 00:15:23,146
Znate,

155
00:15:23,146 --> 00:15:27,525
