Nisam...
- Tom.

174
00:16:49,352 --> 00:16:51,396
Tom, vrati se u krevet.

175
00:16:51,437 --> 00:16:55,190
Sanjao sam taj san
- u redu je, sada sam tu.

176
00:16:55,190 --> 00:16:58,444
Gde si bio, Džone?

177
00:16:58,444 --> 00:17:03,032
Brinuo sam.
- Smiri se sada.

178
00:17:04,699 --> 00:17:07,161
Pretoplo je u ovom krevetu.

179
00:17:07,161 --> 00:17:09,496
Bio sam tako uplašen.

180
00:17:09,496 --> 00:17:11,873
Uspanicio sam se.

181
00:17:11,915 --> 00:17:14,543
Hocu da odem odavde.
Smrdi.

182
00:17:14,543 --> 00:17:20,423
